# Go (statshed-server)
/statshed-server
# (The embedded-SPA placeholder re-includes live in the Node section below, AFTER the
# broad `dist/` rule, so they actually take effect — I9.)

# Node / frontend
node_modules/
dist/
# Re-include the committed embedded-SPA placeholder that the `dist/` rule above would
# otherwise ignore. Order matters: the dir negation comes first, then ignore the built
# children, then re-include the placeholder files. `make prepare-static` overwrites these
# with the real React build (a local-only change); the placeholder keeps //go:embed
# compiling on a fresh checkout (I9).
!internal/staticfs/dist/
internal/staticfs/dist/*
!internal/staticfs/dist/index.html
!internal/staticfs/dist/assets/
internal/staticfs/dist/assets/*
!internal/staticfs/dist/assets/.gitkeep
coverage/
test-results/
playwright-report/
*.tsbuildinfo
npm-debug.log*

# Editors / OS
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# AI / tooling scratch
.codex/
.remember/
